patthana15.3:1.1_0: Hetuṁ vipākaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nahetu navipāko dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana15.3:2.1_0: Hetuṁ vipākadhammadhammaṁ paṭicca nahetu navipākadhammadhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana15.3:3.1_0: Nahetuṁ nevavipākanavipākadhammadhammaṁ paṭicca nanahetu nanevavipākanavipākadhammadhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
